，一见钟情，火速登记结婚，并于第二年生育一子王宝宝，由于婚前了解甚少，婚后的生活琐碎加上经济压力，双方双双去市里打工，将孩子交由王爷爷（老王父亲）代为抚养。 一晃几年过去，老王和小花争吵不断，关系难以缓和，遂起诉至法院要求离婚。 庭审中，老王同意离婚，但双方均拒绝抚养孩子，小花称收入太低无力抚养，老王则称「凭啥你不要？必须你要！你自己生的，自己养」。主张让王宝宝继续跟着王爷爷生活，老王和小花每个月各支付抚养费 500 元，王爷爷拒绝抚养王宝宝，最终法庭判决双方不准离婚，在双方协商好孩子抚养权问题后再另行主张离婚。 来源：北京青年报、星视频"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-8d0c1de7ab4b920711d917e203d25e44_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "367 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/535743908"}}, "attached_info": "ClUIu5rr356MztNKEAMaCDgxMzM2MTAyIMH24JQGMDw4sQVAAnIJNTM1NzQzOTA4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "3_1654262590.4967198", "card_id": "Q_529701503", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 226}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "网传中国第三艘航母即将下水，它将带来哪些重大突破？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "全球最大常规航母：美国黯然退场，中国蓄势待发"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-e65332c1c57fe4e912ac0695a6d4fc19_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "339 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/529701503"}}, "attached_info": "ClUIu5rr356MztNKEAMaCDc5OTkzNDc4IPyYkpMGMDU45QRAA3IJNTI5NzAxNTAzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "4_1654262590.4974139", "card_id": "Q_493594684", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 223}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如果永生人类细胞「海拉细胞」泄露了会有危险吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "（不懂就问）这东西会不会在自然界中无限繁殖，出现难以置信的后果。或者变异出不可思议的新物种？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-e85c759941c5eda7721f39fc2f94c519_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "310 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type":